    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪谈系恐怖悬疑游戏。女大学生琍琍，他暗恋的小涵失踪了！琍琍越探索真相，小涵男友的嫌疑就越大！而这背后，又涉及「食人小男孩」这则怪谈…… </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2.5D运镜・临场感十足</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采用2.5D运镜，使探索更有临场感。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/f2e5745b019bb751d988a94f95836bfc.poster.avif?t=1764863221\" width=632 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/f2e5745b019bb751d988a94f95836bfc.webm?t=1764863221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/f2e5745b019bb751d988a94f95836bfc.mp4?t=1764863221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>搜集线索・揭露真相</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >藉调查对象、与NPC对话来推进剧情，以揭露小涵失踪的真相。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/8ff441debc7898e5f3013603590bf453.poster.avif?t=1764863221\" width=632 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/8ff441debc7898e5f3013603590bf453.webm?t=1764863221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/8ff441debc7898e5f3013603590bf453.mp4?t=1764863221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三种结局・由你决定</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >琍琍与小涵将面临什么样的命运，取决于玩家的选择。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/83fc469f3d3366ec8ee60b437741b659.poster.avif?t=1764863221\" width=632 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/83fc469f3d3366ec8ee60b437741b659.webm?t=1764863221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/83fc469f3d3366ec8ee60b437741b659.mp4?t=1764863221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>改编自TRPG跑团纪录</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本故事是基于开发者与朋友跑TRPG团的纪录，大幅改编而成的；原始的TRPG剧本是マリコロ（Marikoro）的《首切り様》（斩首大人），改编已征得其同意。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/34bb97d10a32159a2138d6173fef95f8.avif?t=1764863221\" width=300 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>琍琍</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女大学生，暗恋自己的闺密小涵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「我要……去找小涵！」</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/c3e59f1eeec60d5e12f1882c75e568f4.avif?t=1764863221\" width=300 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小涵</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失踪的女大学生，最近刚交了一个男友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「我的男友瞒着我什么秘密……」</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/7c83dee3c128815199070e19b9d0c9ae.avif?t=1764863221\" width=300 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小涵的男友</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他自称丧失记忆，小涵也不知道他的来历。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「我是小涵的男朋友，现在是，以后也会是。」</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/5d485b0ef379b04ce9d8073453efa6e7.avif?t=1764863221\" width=300 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>阿元与小玉</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >协寻小涵的除灵二人组，看起来不像好人……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「『善良』是救不了任何人的。」</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084180/extras/0c1a966658fa2573898760c84c657368.avif?t=1764863221\" width=300 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>食人小男孩</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在怪谈中登场的「恶灵」，会咬断受害者的脖子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直播与游戏实况之规范</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许直播与游戏实况。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许营利，但仅限于以影音网站的功能营利。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若能在直播或游戏实况的标题加入游戏名称，或在说明栏列出Steam页面的连结，我方将不胜感激。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直播与游戏实况所导致的任何损害，我方概不负责。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本规范如有变更，恕不另行通知。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >注意</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏使用わたおきば（ Wataokiba）的可商用立绘素材，并遵守其利用规约。</p>",
